description: Laboratorium Theatrum - An Exhibition for Stones, Plants and Touch Screens. A landscape of a possible future, an incomplete ruin that is being overrun daily by a wide ecosystem. Several plants return to their original landscape inside a building closed to bars in the middle of the Brazilian cerrado. In this place there is a permanent exhibition physically inaccessible to the public, these works are only accessible on NFTs on HIC ET NUNC. Brazil,2018-2021
